data.description: Perfect Starter Home! Explore 203 Canadawa Rd in the scenic Highland Lakes, NJ offering 5 lakes, 7 beaches, 2 parks, and plenty of activities all year around! This delightful ranch includes 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom, a warm living room with a wood-burning fireplace and a kitchen that leads to a deck overlooking a large yard with a fire pit and shed. The basement offers ample storage space along with a washer and dryer! Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!
